title: Sister O'dell, Kylie Jenner, Sean Carter, Trump Exam and more.
itunes:title: Sister O'dell, Kylie Jenner, Sean Carter, Trump Exam and more.
description:
Good morning and welcome to the ride! Today we are grateful for the present. Somebody in the crew may have stomach issues and Sister O'dell is here with the remedy. Kylie Jenner could be a control freak. Morris Day is still COOL. Sean Carter was in Hollywood with Alicia Keys. Thanksgiving sometimes brings unique family members. The crew discuss 45's medical examination and Steve tells the world that he is cuter than Trump. What is more important in a Christmas gift, its value or the thought behind it? Today in Closing Remarks, Big Dog reminds us of our unique relationship with God, plus more.
